{dede:field name='body'}<div class=TRS_Editor><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><span style="font-family: 宋体">　　</span><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">据美国</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">space</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">网站</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">2013</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">7</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">19</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">日报道</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">, NASA</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">已经批准拨款研发</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">10</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">项富有想象力的技术概念，并希望借此形成太空科学与探索的重大突破。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"> </span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　这</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">12</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">项概念属于</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">NASA</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">“创新先进概念”（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">NIAC</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">）项目中阶段</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">1</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">的工作，具有雄心且呈现多样性。其中一个目标是打造生物材料，例如利用</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">3D</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">打印机打印人体组织；另一个提议将研究宇航员火星之旅中的深度睡眠麻木问题。阶段</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">1</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">合同价值约</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">10</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">万美元，研究团队将实施为期</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">9</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">个月的初步分析研究，之后可申请阶段</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">2</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">50</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">万美元，进行为期两年多的方案研究。</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　这</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">12</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">个入选概念及其主要参与者包括：</span><span style="font-size: 12pt"> </span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">1</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">、脉冲裂变</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">-</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">聚变（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">PuFF</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">）推进系统（罗伯·亚当斯，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">NASA</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">马歇尔航天飞行中心）；</span><span style="font-size: 12pt"> </span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">2</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">、用于人类停留火星的能引发麻木的转移栖息地（约翰·布拉德福德，太空工作室工程公司）</span><span style="font-size: 12pt"> </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">；</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">3</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">、二维行星行星表面着陆器（哈米德·赫马提，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">NASA</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">喷气推进实验室）；</span><span style="font-size: 12pt"> </span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">4</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">、可实现立方体卫星探测太阳系的双模推进系统（南森·杰瑞德，大学太空研究协会）；</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">5</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">、发展适用的张拉整体结构：太空经济的新演算（安东尼·朗文）</span><span style="font-size: 12pt"> </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">；</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">6</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">、作为“</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">X</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">”解决方案的永恒飞行（马克·摩尔，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">NASA</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">兰利研究中心）；</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">7</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">、太阳系小天体与银河宇宙射线次生粒子簇射之间的深度映射（托马斯·普雷蒂曼，行星科学研究所）；</span><span style="font-size: 12pt"> </span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">8</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">、从稀薄空气提取生物材料：原位、按需打印先进的生物复合材料（林恩·罗斯柴尔德，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">NASA</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">艾姆斯研究中心）</span><span style="font-size: 12pt"> </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">；</span><span style="font-size: 12pt"> </span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">9</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">、等离子动力推进使纳卫星</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">/</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">皮卫星能力发生革命性变化（约书亚·罗韦，密苏里大学罗拉分校）；</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">10</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">、极端环境变压器（艾德里安·斯托伊卡，喷气推进实验室）；</span><span style="font-size: 12pt"> </span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">11</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">、直径</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">10</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">米的亚轨道大气球反射器（克里斯托弗·沃克，亚利桑那大学）；</span><span style="font-size: 12pt"> </span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">　　</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">12</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">、低质平面光子成像传感器（本·优，加州大学戴维斯分校）。</span><span style="font-size: 12pt"> </span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 20pt" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">NIAC</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">项目于</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">年开始实施。最初的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">NIAC</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">指代</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">NASA</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">先进概念研究所，运行时间为</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">1998</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">~2007</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">年；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">2008</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">年，美国国会要求美国国家研究委员会调查</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">NIAC</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">的有效性和重要性。评估结果使该项目在几年之后得以重组。</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 资料来源：</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all; line-height: 20pt; text-align: left" align="justify"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;